    <item>
      <title>Bank of England Speeches Dataset</title>
      <link>https://michelescottodivettimo.eu/project/bankofengland/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://michelescottodivettimo.eu/project/bankofengland/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This page contains the dataset of speeches of Bank of England officials initially collected for &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1111/gove.70103&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Scotto di Vettimo and Koop (2025)&lt;/a&gt;.
The dataset has been compiled by scraping the Bank of England website, and manually annotating a number of relevant covariates for each speech.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;centerbank-of-england-officials-deliver-speeches-around-the-world-and-across-the-ukcenter&#34;&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bank of England officials deliver speeches around the world and across the UK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div style=&#34;display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:0px; margin-bottom:30px;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://michelescottodivettimo.eu/boe/speeches_locs.gif&#34;
          width=&#34;50%&#34; height=&#34;350&#34;
          frameborder=&#34;0&#34; scrolling=&#34;no&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
  &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://michelescottodivettimo.eu/boe/speeches_bars.gif&#34;
          width=&#34;50%&#34; height=&#34;350&#34;
          frameborder=&#34;0&#34; scrolling=&#34;no&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The dataset features &lt;strong&gt;1,390 speeches&lt;/strong&gt; from Bank officials between &lt;strong&gt;May 1997&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;June 2025&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The dataset is available from the UK Data Service free of charge for academic research and personal non-commercial use.
It can be downloaded by clicking the button on top of this page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;citation&#34;&gt;Citation&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When using this data, please cite:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scotto di Vettimo, M. &amp;amp; Koop, C. (2025) &amp;ldquo;Technocrats, reputation, and responsiveness in policy explanation&amp;rdquo;, &lt;em&gt;Governance&lt;/em&gt;, 39(1), e70103. DOI: &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1111/gove.70103&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;10.1111/gove.70103&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The replication package for this paper is available &lt;a href=&#34;https://reshare.ukdataservice.ac.uk/858235/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This page is updated with data collected up to June 2025.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
